\fB-shiftjis\fR
use Shift_JIS for both input and output
.SS Miscellaneous
  
.TP
\fB-version\fR, \fB-v\fR
show the version of Tidy
.TP
\fB-help\fR, \fB-h\fR, \fB-?\fR
list the command line options
.TP
\fB-help-config\fR
list all configuration options
.TP
